Cinematic ENB by Black-Wolf v1.0

Features :

  • Subtle depth of field (As you can see in the screenshots there are no Depth of field effects because the hud and viewmodel are disabled)
  • Subtle Bloom (Mixes with the in-game bloom perfectly)
  • Dark Ambient Occlusion (SSAO)
  • Dark gritty desaturated ambient color correction
  • Motion blur

Installation :

  • Extract the files inside the folder called Counter-Strike Source into your main CS:S directory

This ENB can eat up to 10 FPS do not use this enchancer if you have a bad PC

Warning! This ENB hasn't been used in online matches and was only used in offline mode. I am not responsible for any VAC bans. Use at your own risk!

Please test it in-game before rating thank you!
